  "tarball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/andreasgriffin/bitcoin-safe/tarball/2.0.0",
  "zipball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/andreasgriffin/bitcoin-safe/zipball/2.0.0",
  "body": "### Highlights\r\n\r\n- **Compact Block Filters by default**  \r\n  Compact Block Filters are now the default network option, with a migration notification for existing users.     [PR #559](https://github.com/andreasgriffin/bitcoin-safe/pull/559), [PR #626](https://github.com/andreasgriffin/bitcoin-safe/pull/626)  Big thanks to @rustaceanrob \r\n\r\n- **Redesigned Wallet Setup Wizard**  \r\n  The wallet setup flow has been rebuilt for a clearer and more polished onboarding experience together with @design-rrr .    [PR #627](https://github.com/andreasgriffin/bitcoin-safe/pull/627)  \r\n\r\n- **Redesigned Transaction Signing** \r\n  The signing UI focusses now on devices to achieve the cleanest UI for the different connection types QR, USB, Bluetooth, File, and Share via Chat&Sync   together with @design-rrr   [PR #639](https://github.com/andreasgriffin/bitcoin-safe/pull/639)\r\n\r\n- **Updated device support**  \r\n  Support for  MK5 and Trezor Safe 7    [PR #596](https://github.com/andreasgriffin/bitcoin-safe/pull/596), [PR #598](https://github.com/andreasgriffin/bitcoin-safe/pull/598) \r\n\r\n- **30% faster** animated QR codes for quicker scanning\r\n\r\n- Chat messages now have a [send status icon](https://github.com/andreasgriffin/bitcoin-safe/pull/743)\r\n\r\n- Added \ud83c\uddee\ud83c\uddf3 [Tamil](https://github.com/andreasgriffin/bitcoin-safe/pull/731) language and more translation improvements \r\n\r\n\r\n### Check out \r\n\r\n- www.bitcoin-safe.org\r\n- \ud83c\udf0d Community forum: [substr](https://substr.network/s/bitcoin-safe)\r\n- Follow on [nostr](https://yakihonne.com/profile/nprofile1qqsyz7tjgwuarktk88qvlnkzue3ja52c3e64s7pcdwj52egphdfll0cq9934g) or [X](https://x.com/BitcoinSafeOrg)\r\n\r\n####  Verify signature\r\n\r\nImport my [public key](https://keys.openpgp.org/vks/v1/by-fingerprint/2759AA7148568ECCB03B76301D82124B440F612D) and [verify](https://bitcoin-safe.org/en/download/#verify-signature) the signature.\r\n\r\n",
